Name: Percentage of 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' out of all activity executions in the event log
Metric: Percentage of 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' out of all cases

Name: Frequency of 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' occurring as the first activity in a case
Metric: Frequency of activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Percentage of process variants that start with 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'
Metric: Percentage of 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' out of all cases

Name: Number of times 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' is immediately followed by 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion'
Metric: Number of 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' activities for cases where activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' occurs

Name: Percentage of 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' that are followed at any point in the trace by 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'
Metric: Percentage of 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' out of all 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Ratio of 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' to 'Revised Manuscript Submission Confirmation' occurrences
Metric: Percentage of 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' out of all 'Revised Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Frequency of 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' in cases that eventually reach 'SW-EIC Accept'
Metric: Number of 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' activities for cases where activity 'SW-EIC Accept' occurs

Name: Percentage of cases containing 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' that also contain at least one reviewer-related activity (e.g., 'SW-Reviewer Agreed', 'SW-Reviewer Declined', or 'SW-Reviewer No Response')
Metric: Percentage of 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' out of all 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Number of distinct cases in which 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' appears
Metric: Number of 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' activities

Name: Percentage of 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' activities that occur before any plagiarism check activity (e.g., 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed')
Metric: Percentage of 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' out of all 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed'

Name: Frequency of 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' appearing in variants that lead to a rejection outcome (e.g., 'SW-EIC Reject' or 'SW-EIC Reject & Resubmit')
Metric: Number of 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' activities for cases where activity 'SW-EIC Reject' occurs

Name: Percentage of 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' that are part of traces containing more than three reviewer assignment attempts ('SW-AE Assign Reviewers')
Metric: Percentage of 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' out of all 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Ratio of the frequency of 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' to the frequency of 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'
Metric: Percentage of 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' out of all 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Number of times 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' occurs without being followed by 'SW-Checklist Completed' within the same trace
Metric: Number of 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' activities for cases where activity 'SW-Checklist Completed' does not occur

Name: Percentage of all submissions confirmed via 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' that result in at least one instance of 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'
Metric: Percentage of 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' out of all 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'
